title: Ryan Tannehill is bad
description: Ryan Tannehill is bad and will get replaced this season at QB. I don't think he's good.

title: Austin Ekeler is good
description: Austin Ekeler is good and will play well this season. As long as he stays healthy, victories will ensue.

title: Jordan Love, who knows?
description: I'm unsure if Jordan Love is good or bad. He was kind of bad against the Chiefs, but good against the Eagles. Time will tell...
